title: Free Champions Don't Change
body: I'm now level 10 and my free weekly champions have not changed ever since my first week. I'm tired of seeing the same champions. Is this a bug? Or, is this something I did wrong?

replies.body: You're almost there! One more level and you'll be able to play with the free rotating Champions. In which you can always check out[ Here](https://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/champions-skins/free-rotation).
You get access to the free weekly rotation once you reach level 11
